{"tid":95290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鷹眼、緋紅女巫私下交情超好！大方親臉頰、喝同一杯可可等互動超可愛","createTime":"2017-01-26T01:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T17:01:07.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93762914413af4d57bfea1ba318d93a8b9541e21","tid":95290,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:55:46.000Z","msg":"MARVEL FANS們一定對「鷹眼」傑瑞米雷納（Jeremy Renner）還有「緋紅女巫」伊莉莎白歐森（Elizabeth Olsen）不陌生，兩個都是受歡迎的角色，這次他們一同現身在日舞影展上，宣傳合作的新電影《 Wind River 》，兩個人合作多次感情也變更好，接受訪談時不但能大方親臉頰，還一起去醫院探望癌症病患：<br />\n<br />\n▼傑瑞米跟伊莉莎白在日舞影展上宣傳新電影《 Wind River 》也接受 IMDb 訪問。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62034/5887021325159.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62034%2F5887021325159.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=05a349d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼在受訪的時候，傑瑞米大方地親了伊莉莎白的臉頰，顯示兩個人的交情有多好。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62034/588702121f786.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62034%2F588702121f786.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=0d0b846f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼兩個人近期也一同前往癌症中心探望病人，為病患們加油打氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62034/5887092be276e.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62034%2F5887092be276e.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=42d085df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼鷹眼跟緋紅女巫在日舞影展宣傳期間互動頻頻，還一起享用同一杯可可取暖，超可愛的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62034/5887092cf128b.png?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62034%2F5887092cf128b.png%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=126ee355&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼在新電影《 Wind River 》裡面，傑瑞米飾演一個漁獵部員工，他發現一個年輕女屍體，他將協助伊莉莎白飾演的菜鳥 FBI 探員辦案。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/62034/588709c41f627.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F62034%2F588709c41f627.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=ac376965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鷹眼跟緋紅女巫在漫威電影裡面的時候互動就已經很有趣了，私下的互動怎麼也這麼可愛，果然男女之間是可以有純友誼的！這次在新電影裡面不知道會擦出什麼樣的火花，只能期待它上映了..."},{"pid":"0003a015ab1e8a3573e9ad8c33de8adc10be0d36","tid":95290,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"條友唔駛做特工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29880c16d708de961ae991af440680121120550f","tid":95290,"uid":40306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好sweet"},{"pid":"969105b3bbe6f33e66bd9ee33c499acf19a507b8","tid":95290,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:56:49.000Z","msg":"隊長<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1145dbd79b751b118e917b9977a3b8a2bb23558c","tid":95290,"uid":51041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"條女勁撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bb4e5d78dd2fc3415da169936c6fa4579f8a30","tid":95290,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T06:39:29.000Z","msg":"之前明明傳同洛基，襯好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c517883f718c02eca7b95d5fd2e685ebe1d3f60","tid":95290,"uid":18200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"女巫<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b826d114f96ce98faf4d12867b8ecd0247fb4d7","tid":95290,"uid":77755,